  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK264">
<l>oṉṉārt teṟalu muvantārai yākkalu</l>
<l> meṇṇiṟ ṟavattāṉ varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If (the ascetic) desire the destruction of his enemies, or the aggrandizement of his friends, it will be effected by (the power of) his austerities.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
